From 7f8e1b17905b826a27e15aa69ab5dfa142944f0c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 07:54:13 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] refactor(mdns): replace dnssd2 and mdns-js with
 @astronautlabs/mdns

Consolidates advertising and discovery onto a single pure-TypeScript
mDNS/DNS-SD implementation with no native dependencies. The previous
optional native `mdns` fallback is no longer needed.
---
 package.json     |  3 +--
 src/discovery.js | 26 ++++++++++++--------------
 src/mdns.js      | 23 ++++++-----------------
 3 files changed, 19 insertions(+), 33 deletions(-)

